data.description: Over 7 acres in a secluded valley just minutes from Cripple Creek Colorado. Plenty of room to do what you want with this mountain property. Accessible via a private road just off of Teller 1. Lots of trees and peace and quite. This would be a great location to clear some room for an RV. Come and make this your Colorado Dream spot.  This property is being sold via online auction. The starting bid is $20,000.00.  Registered bidders can go an see the property at any time during the auction. Online Only Auction Opens on Friday, July 1st, 2022 at 8am. Ending Monday, Aug 1st @ 4 PM MST. For more info visit www.timberlinerealtyinc.com
